mods.abstract: The California Magazine of Western Square and Round Dancing by the Square Dancers of Southern California. This edition includes a table of contents which lists the following: "From the Floor", "Square Dance Date Book", "On the Record", "What are they Dancing?", "As I See It", "Gold Ribbon Report-Extended Basics Program", "Feature Fashion", "Square Dancing Away from Home by Madeline Allen", "The Dancers' Walkthru", "DIALOG: Singing Calls", "round Dance Teaching, Part IV-by Ken & Carol Guyre", "National Convention", "Round the World of Square Dancing", "Workshop", "Style Series", "Caller of the Month: Beryl Main", "Current Best Sellers", and "Experimental Lab".
